Award-winning rapper Nicki Minaj has confirmed she is now married. Minaj confirmed the news of her marriage to Kenneth Petty on her Instagram page. She revealed that they got married officially on 21 October, 2019. This was shared along with a video of two hats written bride and groom and cups written Mr and Mrs. The rapper had earlier announced her wedding to her boyfriend, Kenneth Petty. She said she and boyfriend Kenneth Petty would be married in “about 80 days.” Video:   👰🏽🤵🏽😢🙏🏽🎀 Onika Tanya Maraj-Petty 10•21•19 A post shared by  Barbie (@nickiminaj) on Oct 21, 2019 at 8:22pm PDT  Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.